    <section_number>23B</section_number>
    <catch_line>Notice Of Abatements</catch_line>
    <order_by>23B</order_by>
    <text>
        The assessors shall, as often as once a month, notify the auditor or similar officer in cities and towns, the town accountant, if any, otherwise the town treasurer, of the amounts of abatements of taxes.
    </text>
